title: 4 out of 5 doctors - 2nd opinion [New wave 1982]
description:
4 out of 5 doctors - 2nd opinion

This album is fantastic, truly a lost gem. 2nd LP by 4 out of 5 doctors but the debut is about just as good (4.5 stars on that one).  Great band. They deserved much more attention than they got back then.
